#Repost @kickingitwithshekinah
・・・
* I don’t own copyrights to this music *

Better Days are coming for Shekinah! 🙏🏾🤍 if I could give her a big hug right now I would because she’s been through so much just to be where she is now !!! Shekinah had to let go of some things just to be where she is now and that’s what y’all are failing to realize... Y’all think it’s so easy to become successful and famous but there’s a lot that comes with that responsibility! Shekinah is a hard working woman that worked for her spot and things in life 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾

One day she will receive her blessings back . For the people who used her and stolen from her .  God is going to continue to bless her because he knows her heart and he knows her story and change in life and that’s all that matters . 

I can’t wait for her to blow out with a Big Bang !!!!!! Her blessings are on the way 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾

Proverbs 3:5-6

 Trust in the Lord with all your heart and lean not on your own understanding; in all your ways submit to him, and he will make your paths straight.

He’s going to make a way for shekinah!
 WATCH 🗣🗣🗣🗣🗣🗣👋🏾👋🏾👋🏾
